OL,3,CBusinesses 'crying out' for Scottish
OL,4,Cvisas to boost workforce, says SNP MP
OL,6,FBusinesses are "crying out" for
OL,7,FScottish visas, an SNP MP has said, as
OL,8,Fhe claimed a managed migration scheme
OL,9,Fcould boost Scotland's economic growth.
OL,11,FStephen Gethins argued the UK's
OL,12,Fcurrent "one-size fits all" approach
OL,13,Fto immigration is not working, ahead
OL,14,Fof the second reading of his
OL,15,FDevolution (Immigration) (Scotland)
OL,16,FBill on Friday.
