OL,3,CBusinesses 'crying out' for Scottish
OL,4,Cvisas to boost workforce, says SNP MP
OL,6,FThe MP for Arbroath and Broughty Ferry
OL,7,Fsaid his private member's Bill
OL,8,Fproposes to devolve more powers over
OL,9,Fimmigration to Holyrood, to increase
OL,10,FScotland's workforce in the
OL,11,Fhospitality, tourism and care sectors.
OL,13,FSpeaking to the PA news agency, he
OL,14,Fsaid: "Having a one-size fits all
OL,15,Fapproach to migration is not something
OL,16,Fthat makes for good policy.
