OL,3,CBusinesses 'crying out' for Scottish
OL,4,Cvisas to boost workforce, says SNP MP
OL,6,F"Currently, we are making policy that
OL,7,Fis taking into account the South East
OL,8,Fof England, and not taking into
OL,9,Faccount, for example, parts of
OL,10,FScotland that are crying out for a
OL,11,Fgreater workforce.
OL,13,F"And migration has always driven
OL,14,Feconomic growth."
OL,16,FHe added: "We're not talking about
OL,17,Funcontrolled migration, we're talking
OL,18,Fabout areas that are good for
OL,19,Fbusiness, and that's why so many
OL,20,Fbusinesses and industry bodies are
OL,21,Fcalling for this very measure.
