OL,6,FMr Gethins continued: "This is about
OL,7,Fmanaged migration, but instead of
OL,8,Fdoing the Boris Johnson approach of
OL,9,Fjust throwing open the doors and
OL,10,Fhaving no benefit for Scotland, let's
OL,11,Fsee where it can benefit specific
OL,12,Fsectors."
OL,14,FThe specific details of what a
OL,15,FScottish visa would entail could be
OL,16,Fdecided in collaboration with other
OL,17,Fpolitical parties, Mr Gethins said.
